2.title: Super resolution using GAN
2.content: This project is mainly deploying GAN for generating high fedility MRI images . The result of SR could be extend for consequent applications, e.g. data augmentation, and these result were shown in OHBM 2022 and MIDL.

4.title: About me
4.content: I’m currently a Ph.D. student at Universität Tübingen and Max Planck Institute for Biological Cybernetics. My current research focus is generative models using deep learning methods(e.g. GAN, score-match model, etc.) and its application on Medical Image data, especially MRI(~9.4Tesla). I was mainly educated in major of Mechanical Engineering in Hongkong Polytechnic University.
